/*
 * =================================================================
 * D4 - NEW PERIPHERAL DEVICE (WITH SPI DISPLAY) - WI-FI VERSION
 * =================================================================
 *
 * Role:
 * 1. Acts as a TCP client to send data to D1.
 * 2. Hosts a TCP server to listen for data and warnings from D1.
 * 3. Reads compass and sends heading, SOS status, and Wi-Fi RSSI.
 * 4. Displays its status and relative data from D1 using bitmaps.
 * 5. On warning: vibrates, blinks LED, and displays alert on SPI OLED.
 *
 * HARDWARE: ESP32, QMC5883L, 0.96" SPI OLED, Button, Vibration Motor, LED
 */

